{
  "stem": "6526.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, they, they could see that they're not going to be sent right away to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Majdanek?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wasn't seen as I am down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I was gassed, and I couldn't-- they sent us to work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I couldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they asked, who is sick to go to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had no choice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If I'm not going to go to the hospital, I take a chance.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Maybe there's a hospital.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But if I'm going to remain there, I'm going to be shot on the-- on the spot there because I [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When I came into the hospital, I found a man who was a son-of-law of people that we knew.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was brought from Warsaw in 1942.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I already came there in 1943.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he was already-- and he gave me some pointers and-- but he wasn't there long.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because I didn't-- when I came out of the-- out of the hospital alive, he wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I couldn't see him again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe a week.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were doctors.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they were Poles.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were Poles.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe they were Jewish, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I remember that they gave me a drink to get phlegm down, because I was all plugged up.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He gave me a drink like a good beer, a, a liqueur-- like a cognac or something.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when he gave me that, the whole thing got me so soft.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I felt so good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I begged him for more.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He says, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But they had me on a diet and give me a hard boiled egg [LAUGHS] in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well, I came out of hospital alive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was in Majdanek for almost three months.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I got a number in Majdanek, but not a tattooed number.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
